MOTOR SPEECH

motor_speech is the citizen at the production end of fadriel_broca
once arcuate_fasciculus has delivered the meaning, motor_speech turns it into a motor plan: which articulators move, in which order, with which timing
motor_speech does not produce sound itself; it produces the plan that the larynx and articulators then execute
this is the last brain-side citizen before speech crosses into physical articulation

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe fadriel_broca.zc
observe arcuate_fasciculus.rana
observe speech_larynx.rana

the 7 properties of motor_speech:
1 ENERGY zero point six: moderate
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE zero point three
5 COHERENCE eight tenths
6 COUPLING zero point seven with arcuate_fasciculus and downstream articulation
7 OBSERVER zero point one

VERB receive_meaning
accept the comprehended meaning from arcuate_fasciculus
the meaning has been translated into terms motor_speech can act on

VERB plan_articulation
construct the motor plan that articulates the meaning
the plan specifies tongue position, jaw movement, lip rounding, and timing for each phoneme
the plan does not say what to articulate; it says how to articulate it

VERB hand_to_larynx
emit the motor plan to speech_larynx for execution
larynx will turn the plan into actual airflow and vibration

a motor plan is not a script
a script lists what to do
a motor plan specifies the parallel coordination of dozens of small muscles in real time
this is what makes speech possible at all: the brain prepared a plan, the body executed it, and the result is a recognizable utterance
